2
00:01:41,250 --> 00:01:42,625
[glass shatters]

3
00:01:50,541 --> 00:01:53,083
It's no use...

4
00:01:53,166 --> 00:01:55,125
I don't feel any better.

5
00:01:58,041 --> 00:02:01,125
It's just...
unforgiveable...

6
00:02:04,041 --> 00:02:07,541
That anyone else could be
closer to Ellis than me.

7
00:02:07,625 --> 00:02:08,666
[L.A. chuckles]

8
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:11,166
Achoo!

9
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:12,916
Are you catching a cold?

10
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,916
[NADIE] Nah, somebody's
probably just talking about me.

11
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,083
"Hey, did you hear about that
sexy bounty hunter chick?"

12
00:02:19,166 --> 00:02:21,041
"Oh yeah, I hear
she's smoking hot!

13
00:02:21,125 --> 00:02:24,458
She's got a killer figure and
a mind as sharp as a tack."

14
00:02:24,541 --> 00:02:26,333
"Whoo... What I wouldn't give

15
00:02:26,416 --> 00:02:29,375
to run into a woman like
that just once in my life."

16
00:02:29,458 --> 00:02:30,958
Then why don't
you chop these?

17
00:02:31,041 --> 00:02:31,750
[NADIE] Wha...?

18
00:02:31,833 --> 00:02:34,333
With your
sharp mind.

19
00:02:34,416 --> 00:02:35,583
[POLICEMAN A grunts]

20
00:02:36,583 --> 00:02:38,083
What the hell...?

21
00:02:38,166 --> 00:02:39,875
