22
00:02:42,875 --> 00:02:44,541
[L.A.] Unforgiveable.

23
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:51,750
[L.A. sighs]

24
00:02:51,833 --> 00:02:54,625
[POLICEMAN A gasps]

25
00:02:54,708 --> 00:02:56,166
[BLUE-EYES] And then...

26
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:59,791
