overtake his psyche.

27
00:02:59,875 --> 00:03:00,708
[L.A. chuckles]

28
00:03:00,791 --> 00:03:02,833
[gun cocks]

29
00:03:19,541 --> 00:03:20,208
[ELLIS] What'd they say?

30
00:03:20,291 --> 00:03:22,000
