31
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:25,208
I guess he caused some
trouble last night.

32
00:03:25,291 --> 00:03:26,916
Ooh. What did he do?

33
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,000
[NADIE] Yeah, please
don't make me repeat it.

34
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,541
'kay I won't.

35
00:03:30,625 --> 00:03:32,916
So... Wanna find a motel?

36
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,541
[POLICEMAN A] Don't bother
looking for a place to stay.

37
00:03:35,625 --> 00:03:37,291
We'd like you
to come with us.

38
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:39,708
What...?
How come?

39
