Then we'll arrest
you for obstruction.

42
00:03:46,875 --> 00:03:48,250
[NADIE] Umm...

43
00:03:48,333 --> 00:03:49,458
Heh.

44
00:03:50,875 --> 00:03:52,166
[POLICEMAN B] Oof!

45
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:54,625
