dead no one would miss you.

67
00:05:16,916 --> 00:05:18,708
You were "told?"

68
00:05:18,791 --> 00:05:19,916
[POLICEMAN A] Heh.

69
00:05:21,125 --> 00:05:22,166
Listen...

70
00:05:22,250 --> 00:05:24,375
Believe it or not
I am a gentleman...

71
00:05:24,458 --> 00:05:26,500
Thank your stars for that...

72
00:05:26,583 --> 00:05:29,583
Besides, the last thing I'm
looking for is more trouble.

73
00:05:53,416 --> 00:05:55,375
Someone's playin' 'em.

74
00:05:59,125 --> 00:06:00,083
[POLICEMAN A gasps]

75
00:06:00,166 --> 00:06:01,708
[L.A.] What a letdown.

76
00:06:01,791 --> 00:06:03,500
You didn't kill her.

77
00:06:03,583 --> 00:06:05,416
[POLICEMAN A] Well I'm not you.

78
00:06:07,125 --> 00:06:09,125
Such weak creatures.

79
00:06:19,541 --> 00:06:20,583
[POLICEMAN A]
Once we capture the girl

80
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,125
we'll hand her
over to you...

81
00:06:22,208 --> 00:06:26,083
