Champion of Justice?

83
00:06:28,583 --> 00:06:29,750
[POLICEMAN A] Long as
you don't come back,

84
00:06:29,833 --> 00:06:32,000
we'll forget about your
incident at the bar...

85
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:34,000
