[L.A. giggles]

89
00:06:41,916 --> 00:06:43,458
Hey... Status?

90
00:06:43,541 --> 00:06:45,125
[POLICEMAN B]
Sorry, nothing yet.

91
00:06:45,208 --> 00:06:47,708
I'll let you know
if she turns up here.

92
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:49,750
[POLICEMAN B] Copy that.

93
00:06:49,833 --> 00:06:51,083
Why us?

94
00:06:56,083 --> 00:06:57,666
[POLICEMAN A] Seriously...

95
00:07:09,708 --> 00:07:12,625
Ellis is mine
and mine alone.

96
00:07:40,083 --> 00:07:41,375
Don't run off.

97
00:07:43,625 --> 00:07:45,250
Where're you going?

98
00:07:45,333 --> 00:07:47,583
To rescue Nadie.

99
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:48,500
[RICARDO] How...?

100
00:07:48,583 --> 00:07:51,166
