[ELLIS] And I've never done
anything to help her.

112
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:29,208
[RICARDO] Remember,
you're the one they want.

113
00:08:29,291 --> 00:08:31,083
[ELLIS] I'm going.

114
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:38,333
Lirio...

115
