128
00:09:57,458 --> 00:09:58,791
[ROSENBERG chuckles]

129
00:09:58,875 --> 00:10:00,833
[ROSENBERG] Truth is, so do I.

130
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:03,291
[MELISSA] Heh. That is true...

131
00:10:03,375 --> 00:10:07,250
For some reason,
I'm never able to lie to you.

132
00:10:07,333 --> 00:10:09,208
[ROSENBERG]
That's the way it should be.

133
00:10:09,291 --> 00:10:11,333
[MELISSA] I love you, Doug.

134
00:10:11,416 --> 00:10:12,625
[ROSENBERG] Melissa.

135
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:15,083
[gunshot]

136
00:10:16,541 --> 00:10:19,083
[bullet shells clatter]

137
