[NADIE] Hey, jerks...!

138
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:31,208
Dinner?!

139
00:10:31,291 --> 00:10:33,166
Dumb bastards...

140
00:10:33,250 --> 00:10:36,583
My stomach is seconds
away from eating itself.

141
00:10:36,666 --> 00:10:39,583
