142
00:10:39,666 --> 00:10:40,291
Oh!

143
00:10:40,375 --> 00:10:44,083
Hey... doesn't hurt.

144
00:10:44,166 --> 00:10:46,666
[NADIE] Warrr-dennn...!

145
00:10:52,625 --> 00:10:53,333
[RICARDO] Nadie.

146
00:10:53,416 --> 00:10:55,708
[NADIE gasps]

147
00:10:55,791 --> 00:10:56,708
[NADIE] Ricardo?

148
00:10:56,791 --> 00:10:58,458
We're bustin' you out.

149
00:10:58,541 --> 00:10:59,750
[NADIE] What about Ellis?

150
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:00,750
Is she okay?

151
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,125
Yeah, she's fine.

152
00:11:02,208 --> 00:11:03,125
[NADIE sighs]

153
00:11:03,208 --> 00:11:04,833
Thank God.

154
00:11:04,916 --> 00:11:06,291
[RICARDO] She wants to save you.

155
00:11:06,375 --> 00:11:07,666
[NADIE gasps]

156
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:10,125
[RICARDO] That's what she said.

157
00:11:10,208 --> 00:11:12,041
[NADIE] Don't let her be stupid.

158
00:11:12,125 --> 00:11:13,833
I won't.

159
00:11:13,916 --> 00:11:16,416
[NADIE] That girl is
honest to a fault.

160
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,875
Well so are you.

161
00:11:17,958 --> 00:11:18,958
[NADIE] Uh...

162
00:11:19,041 --> 00:11:20,083
[RICARDO] You make a good pair.

163
00:11:20,166 --> 00:11:22,375
Wait is that
a compliment...

164
00:11:22,458 --> 00:11:24,208
...or an insult?

165
00:11:24,291 --> 00:11:25,166
[RICARDO] Kinda both.

166
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:27,416
Heh. We're a good pair, huh?

167
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:28,708
Funny.

168
00:11:30,166 --> 00:11:33,166
[L.A. whimpers]

169
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:35,541
With my Ellis...

170
00:11:38,083 --> 00:11:40,083
"A good pair?!"

171
00:11:41,666 --> 00:11:43,541
No leads yet, huh?

172
00:11:43,625 --> 00:11:46,166
[POLICEMAN B] Nada.

173
00:11:46,250 --> 00:11:47,208
[POLICEMAN B gasps]

174
00:11:47,291 --> 00:11:48,166
Stupid humans.

175
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:51,791
[POLICEMEN gasp]

176
00:11:51,875 --> 00:11:53,833
[L.A.] So very dull.

177
00:12:15,166 --> 00:12:17,166
[ELLIS pants]

178
00:12:31,291 --> 00:12:32,375
[B-LADY A] Now's our chance.

179
00:12:32,458 --> 00:12:33,750
Not yet.

180
00:12:33,833 --> 00:12:35,291
[B-LADY A] But ma'am...

181
00:12:35,375 --> 00:12:36,791
Not yet.

182
00:12:39,291 --> 00:12:42,416
'kay... Let's move.

183
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:43,500
Ellis?

184
00:12:43,583 --> 00:12:45,583
It's hot.

185
00:12:45,666 --> 00:12:48,083
Without Nadie with me...

186
00:12:48,166 --> 00:12:49,791
It's hot...

187
00:12:51,791 --> 00:12:53,125
It's hot.

188
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,333
L.A. is here.

189
00:13:04,416 --> 00:13:05,750
