190
00:13:30,166 --> 00:13:31,791
[L.A. chuckles]

191
00:13:31,875 --> 00:13:33,500
[L.A.] Nadie.

192
00:13:33,583 --> 00:13:34,958
L.A...

193
00:13:45,958 --> 00:13:47,083
[L.A. chuckles]

194
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,791
The hell...?

195
00:13:50,875 --> 00:13:53,916
I thought we agreed
you'd leave Ellis to me.

196
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,458
[L.A.] Hm...

197
00:13:55,541 --> 00:13:57,875
