198
00:13:57,958 --> 00:13:59,000
[NADIE sighs]

199
00:14:02,208 --> 00:14:03,208
[L.A.] Heh.

200
00:14:07,375 --> 00:14:08,541
[RICARDO gasps]

201
00:14:20,875 --> 00:14:21,958
Ellis.

202
00:14:24,833 --> 00:14:26,125
Ellis?!

203
00:14:26,208 --> 00:14:28,833
[ELLIS] Nadie.

204
00:14:36,208 --> 00:14:39,000
I shouldn't have
left things...

205
00:14:39,083 --> 00:14:41,250
in your hands...

206
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:43,041
or those cops.

207
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:47,125
Humans are such
weak creatures...

208
00:14:47,208 --> 00:14:49,625
So they lean on each other...

209
00:14:49,708 --> 00:14:50,916
Rubbish...

210
00:14:52,458 --> 00:14:53,666
Pathetic!

211
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:55,500
[L.A. laughs]

212
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:58,208
Oh yeah...?
Why'd you leave her with me...

213
00:14:58,291 --> 00:15:00,041
if I'm so weak?

214
00:15:00,125 --> 00:15:01,916
[L.A.] Ah. Well...

215
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,833
I suppose I thought it
would be interesting.

216
00:15:04,916 --> 00:15:06,958
Sure y'did...

217
00:15:07,041 --> 00:15:09,083
Or maybe the truth
is you were scared.

218
00:15:09,166 --> 00:15:11,250
[L.A. gasps]

219
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:12,833
You didn't want to upset Ellis

220
00:15:12,916 --> 00:15:16,041
to the point where
she hates you.

221
00:15:16,125 --> 00:15:18,458
I'm right... aren't I?

222
00:15:23,208 --> 00:15:24,416
[L.A. giggles]

223
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,000
How human of you.

224
00:15:26,083 --> 00:15:27,375
[L.A.] Heh.

225
00:15:32,916 --> 00:15:34,583
I won't miss this time.

226
00:15:34,666 --> 00:15:36,208
Anger...

227
00:15:36,291 --> 00:15:38,583
Very good, that's
even more human.

228
00:15:38,666 --> 00:15:39,708
[L.A. laughs]

229
00:15:43,208 --> 00:15:48,458
[ELLIS panting]

230
00:15:48,541 --> 00:15:49,291
[NADIE] Ellis!

231
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:52,708
[L.A. gasps]

232
00:15:52,791 --> 00:15:54,083
[RICARDO] Nadie!

233
00:15:54,166 --> 00:15:56,583
[ELLIS growls]

234
00:15:56,666 --> 00:15:57,500
[NADIE] Ellis!

235
00:15:57,583 --> 00:15:59,541
[L.A. whimpers]

236
00:16:16,208 --> 00:16:18,458
Hm. Ellis.

237
00:16:26,458 --> 00:16:28,916
Hurt her 'n' I won't
forgive you...

238
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,375
Not ever.

239
00:16:30,458 --> 00:16:31,875
[L.A. gasps]

240
00:16:34,416 --> 00:16:37,500
Ellis.

241
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:40,166
Even when you find out
who she really is?

242
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:41,625
[NADIE gasps]

243
00:16:41,708 --> 00:16:43,000
[ELLIS] Who she--?

244
00:16:43,083 --> 00:16:44,458
You see...

245
00:16:44,541 --> 00:16:47,500
