she says she is.

246
00:16:47,583 --> 00:16:49,166
She's lying to you.

247
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:50,791
Don't!

248
00:16:50,875 --> 00:16:53,583
[L.A.] I'll tell you
the truth, Ellis...

249
00:16:55,291 --> 00:16:57,708
[L.A.] Nadie was...

250
00:16:57,791 --> 00:16:59,916
hired by an organization...

251
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:03,125
