your path in the first place.

252
00:17:03,208 --> 00:17:05,625
She was...

253
00:17:05,708 --> 00:17:07,500
hired to watch you.

254
00:17:20,250 --> 00:17:21,791
[ELLIS] Watch me?

255
00:17:25,583 --> 00:17:27,750
Would you like to go sit
with Mommy and Daddy?

256
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:29,791
[LIRIO giggles]

257
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:54,125
[RICARDO] Nadie.
[NADIE] Huh?

258
00:17:54,208 --> 00:18:02,833
[ELLIS panting]

259
00:18:02,916 --> 00:18:05,041
[L.A. giggles]

260
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:06,791
Ellis.

261
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:19,291
[BLUE-EYES gasps]

262
00:18:19,375 --> 00:18:22,458
[ELLIS panting]

263
00:18:22,541 --> 00:18:25,791
Ellis...
That's good...

264
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,125
[L.A. whimpering]

265
00:18:28,208 --> 00:18:34,166
[NADIE] Whoa!

266
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:35,625
