268
00:18:46,166 --> 00:18:47,583
Nadie.

269
00:18:49,291 --> 00:18:51,000
Ellis.

270
00:18:51,083 --> 00:18:52,416
Nadie.

271
00:18:54,125 --> 00:18:55,875
You're safe...

272
00:18:55,958 --> 00:18:57,875
I'm here.

273
00:18:57,958 --> 00:19:00,583
[ELLIS] Thank you.

274
00:19:00,666 --> 00:19:02,416
Ellis.

275
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,458
[L.A. whimpers]

276
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:18,333
[L.A. sighs]

277
00:19:24,625 --> 00:19:26,083
[ELLIS] Wait.

278
00:19:29,125 --> 00:19:31,833
I'm sorry...

279
00:19:31,916 --> 00:19:35,458
I am, but Nadie is Nadie...

280
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,916
And for me, that's enough...

281
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,375
You see?

282
00:19:42,541 --> 00:19:43,750
[L.A.] A deal's a deal.

283
00:19:43,833 --> 00:19:46,333
I'll take you as
far as Wiñay Marka.

284
00:19:46,416 --> 00:19:49,208
Let's get this over with...

285
00:19:49,291 --> 00:19:50,791
L.A...

286
00:19:59,416 --> 00:20:01,291
Let's end it.

287
00:20:06,041 --> 00:20:07,291
[L.A.] Until then...

288
00:20:07,375 --> 00:20:08,625
Ellis.

289
00:20:33,208 --> 00:20:35,416
We missed our
opportunity, ma'am...

290
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,791
You have my apologies...

291
00:20:37,875 --> 00:20:39,375
Won't happen again.

292
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:03,125
[phone rings]

293
00:21:03,208 --> 00:21:06,000
Yes, I'm here...

294
00:21:06,083 --> 00:21:08,208
Today's report, if you please.

295
00:21:14,291 --> 00:21:17,000
[NADIE exhales]

296
00:21:17,083 --> 00:21:23,041
[ELLIS sleeping]

297
00:21:23,125 --> 00:21:30,833
[NADIE gasps]

298
00:21:30,916 --> 00:21:34,166
Nadie.

299
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:36,416
You saved me...

300
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:38,333
Thank you.

301
00:21:38,416 --> 00:21:41,833
It's okay now...

302
00:21:41,916 --> 00:21:44,750
It's... gonna be all right.

303
00:22:00,208 --> 00:22:02,166
[L.A. crying]

304
00:22:25,875 --> 00:22:27,541
[BLUE-EYES]
Even artificial life forms

305
00:22:27,625 --> 00:22:30,500
develop the capacity
for emotion...

306
00:22:30,583 --> 00:22:32,625
In this regard...

307
00:22:32,708 --> 00:22:35,375
there are no exceptions...

308
00:22:35,458 --> 00:22:36,916
None.

